Italian Wedding Soup

50 min
$15.99
350 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 6

Allergens:

glutendairy

Dietary Tags:

high-proteinlow-carb

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

main

Tags:

soupItaliancomfort food

Description

A comforting soup packed with flavorful meatballs, fresh greens, and hearty broth.

Ingredients

  • ground beef: 1 lb
  • italian sausage: 1/2 lb
  • spinach: 4 cups
  • carrots: 2, diced
  • celery: 2 stalks, diced
  • onion: 1, chopped
  • chicken broth: 8 cups
  • parmesan cheese: 1/2 cup, grated
  • egg: 1
  • bread crumbs: 1/2 cup
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • nutmeg: a pinch
  • italian seasoning: 1 tsp
